				"\"Is it crying?\""
				"\"Perhaps it's just syrup leaking out.\""
				"\"Sugar is a treasure for stopping tears.\""
				"\"It exists in the songs of innocent children.\""
				"\"That's the dream of many.\""
				"\"And my past too.\""
				"\"Has something sweet lost its sweetness?\""
				"\"What a deceptive candy...\""
				"\"Just cry... cry.\""
				"\"After all, it was worth it.\""
				"\"Tears are the past.\""
				"\"But there's no need to be upset.\""
				"\"I'm giving you this crying candy bag.\""
				"\"I hope you won't cry anymore.\""
				"\"Because of that past hope.\""
				"\"Eat the candy bag.\""
				"\"The taste in your mouth may not be as wonderful.\""
				"\"But what truly satisfies is that touch of melancholy.\""
				"\"It's the bittersweet feeling.\""
			]
