		{
			dependencies: ["5F26D9E70BF588CE"]
			description: [
				"Only people who have refused their mortality can consume this food."
				""
				"After consumption:"
				"-> Recover 10 points of hunger"
				"-> Recover 12 points of saturation"
				"-> Gain Midas Touch Effect for 30:00 minutes"
				"-> Gain Eternity III Effect for an unlimited duration"
				"-> Gain Soul Armor II Effect for an unlimited duration"
				"-> Permanently Increases mining speed by 10% (Three times)"
				"-> Permanently increases magic resistance by 50% (Once)"
				""
				"Notes: "
				"-> The Midas Touch Effect makes entities drop gold nuggets on death, the amount increases with the level of the effect."
				"-> The Eternity Effect allows you to retain all current potion effects after your death at the cost of a level of the Eternity Effect itself."
				"-> The Soul Armor Effect grants 2 armor points per level of the effect."
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"“I embrace the purest darkness.”"
				"“It bestows upon me infinite emptiness.”"
				"“At the juncture of life and death.”"
				"“I then understand the principle of eternity.”"
				"“That which is imposed upon me by external things.”"
				"“Ultimately, it does not belong to me.”"
				"Your immortal essence."
				"Flowing through your pale bones."
				"The stone in your hand, burning with an eerie light."
				"It seems to have grown even hotter."
				"You will unravel its mysteries."
				"You will let it accompany you forever."
				"Let it offer its magic."
				"Let it embed itself into your body and soul."
				"“Food is the Way.”"
				"The roadside scenery on the path of darkness."
				"Its secrets are revealed."
				"They are calling to you."
				"Eat!"
				"Eat the creation of witchcraft."
				"Eat the treasures of darkness."
				"Eat the essence of the soul."
				"Eat the forbidden fruit of desire."
				"What you consume will ultimately come with a price. And you bear that price."
				"Thus, you are able to consume it."
			]
			id: "30A929F6CCD01168"
			subtitle: "Transmute your hunger into POWER"
			tasks: [{
				id: "5B47F1D05D64BDCB"
				item: "goetydelight:sundae_of_the_philosophers_potion"
				type: "item"
			}]
			x: -5.5d
			y: 5.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5F26D9E70BF588CE"]
			description: [
				"After consumption:"
				"-> Recover 7 points of hunger"
				"-> Recover 8 points of saturation"
				"-> Gain Nourishing Effect for 5:00 minutes"
				"-> Gain Photosynthesis II Effect for 1:00 minute"
				""
				"Notes:"
				"-> The Nourishing Effect prevents players from getting hungry or losing saturation through exhausting actions, such as running, jumping and attacking mobs."
				"-> The Photosynthesis Effect allows entities to regain health in sunlight, the higher the level the faster the recovery."
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"\"This candy bag gleams with a shimmering light.\""
				"\"The syrup is as glistening as dew.\""
				"\"Exposed to the warm spring sun.\""
				"\"Where do you come from?\""
				"\"It has concealed the sorrow in my heart.\""
				"\"Would you like to hear my story?\""
				"\"The story is long.\""
				"\"Why not?\""
				"\"I see.\""
				"\"Sorrow is the past that has passed.\""
				"\"There's no need to remember meaningless melancholy.\""
				"\"Forget those sorrows.\""
				"\"Cast away those worries.\""
				"\"For the sun rises on the road.\""
				"\"It illuminates the traveler.\""
				"\"The future is coming towards me.\""
				"\"I will eventually leave the present.\""
				"\"The present will become the past.\""
				"\"Just remember the good.\""
				"\"Remembering is hope.\""
				"\"Eat this candy bag.\""
				"\"Remember its advice.\""
			]
