				"-> Gain Piglin Support for 6:00 minutes"
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"\"Messenger of Purgatory.\""
				"\"This is my home turf.\""
				"\"Since you have come,\""
				"\"you will suffer a bloody end.\""
				"\"I will use this blood,\""
				"\"to make the finest wine.\""
				"You slew."
				"that messenger from beyond the realm."
				"Divine blood stained the dust."
				"The sacred fire faded."
				"Though not truly dead,"
				"he was still a defeated foe."
				"When the messenger of the gods fell,"
				"you will profane the cult of the underworld."
				"\"Unprecedented.\""
				"\"A chilling and astonishing brew.\""
				"\"Without any taboos.\""
				"\"That tainted blood, like a nectar.\""
				"\"Still as if in a trance.\""
				"\"Still as if in a frenzy.\""
			]
