		{
			dependencies: ["5F26D9E70BF588CE"]
			description: [
				"It is consumed 3x slower than regular food."
				""
				"After consumption:"
				"-> Recover 8 points of hunger"
				"-> Recover 8 points of saturation"
				"-> Gain Nauseau Effect for 1:40 minutes"
				"-> Gain Poison X Effect for 1:40 minutes"
				"-> Gain Weakness V Effect for 1:40 minutes"
				""
				"Notes:"
				"-> You gain immunity to Nausea after 5 consumptions, immunity to Poison after 10 consumptions and immune to Weakness after 15 consumptions."
				"-> You can feed it to other entities"
				""
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				""
				"\"Is this stuff really edible?\""
				"\"I fed it to a few villagers, and they didn't fare too well.\""
				"\"But according to my research,\""
				"\"with repeated consumption, they can adapt to these poisons.\""
				"\"Perhaps I should let my friend try it first?\""
				"You combine various poisons into a pot."
				"Their appearances are still vaguely discernible."
				"Although you really don't want to eat this filth,"
				"but what can you do? You're a dark sorcerer!"
				"You're fearless!"
				"The more stimulating it is, the happier you are!"
				"True gains often come after hardship."
				"Once you overcome it, you'll no longer be afraid."
				"Faced with this food that has no color, aroma, or taste,"
				"you still open your mouth wide."
				"\"What a satisfying meal!"
				"I must feed this to my friend."
				"Good things must be shared.\""
			]
