				""
				"This recipe can only be made after reading the Vizier's Cookbook."
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"“Those people really know how to enjoy themselves.”"
				"“After all, they were pioneers in dark art.”"
				"“They balanced the deliciousness of reality with the essence of the soul.”"
				"“The essence of deliciousness? That reminds me of something.”"
				"“But ultimately, it all comes down to skill.”"
				"The great chef possesses ambition."
				"He doesn't envy the creations of others."
				"Because—"
				"In the end, it's all mine."
				"That's exactly what you think."
				"So you draw your knife."
				"You cut it into eight pieces."
				"Greedily taking, tirelessly."
				"Just like those who once enjoyed this cake alone."
				"Those who plunder are plundered."
				"But you haven't become like them."
				"Because you will far surpass them!"
				"You wipe the cream from your lips."
				"You gaze into the distance."
			]
