		{
			dependencies: ["1BE9FFCE5E664BAF"]
			description: [
				"Found in treasure chests in The Tomb."
				"Eating time is 2.5x slower than normal food."
				""
				"After consumption:"
				"-> Recover 6 points of hunger"
				"-> Recover 6 points of saturation"
				"-> Gain Cursed Effect for 20 seconds"
				"-> Randomly draws an item from The Tomb's itempool."
				""
				"Notes:"
				"-> The Cursed Effect removes natural life regeneration and prevents healing"
				""
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				""
				"\"It doesn't look like anything edible.\""
				"\"Is it ashes of a dead person?\""
				"\"Or an old lunchbox?\""
				"\"Stir it carefully, and you can find some small trinkets.\""
				"\"Many things have lost their original appearance.\""
				"\"Only the aura of a curse flickers.\""
				"You are in that dark tomb."
				"You open the dusty box."
				"From the crack comes"
				"A mournful cry, unwilling to die."
				"It doesn't last long."
				"It vanishes with the wind in a few breaths."
				"Only a box lies among the old things."
				"Telling of the past."
				"You eat what's in that box."
				"The past reappears in your heart."
				"Including the treasures of the deceased."
				"Hear the mournful cry again."
				"Not from the box."
				"But from your heart."
				"It lingers for a moment."
				"Then it doesn't stay."
			]
